A '''Batag Skiff''' was a type of [[Hapan]] [[Skiff/Legends|skiff]]. [[Lalu Morwan]] owned one. The hatch code for her skiff was "Alophon", and the pilot's code was "Remela". Morwan let [[Aurra Sing/Legends|Aurra Sing]] take the skiff in order to [[Attempted assassination of Allana Solo|attempt to assassinate]] the [[Chume'da]] [[Allana Djo Solo|Allana]], while Morwan rode in the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']]. Its sensors included automatic [[Electromagnetic discharge filter|filters]].

